data.description: This Home is priced to sell. As you enter into this one level 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home you will notice the spacious living room that can meet your entertaining needs. This home can be your forever home with some TLC. Primary bedroom is large with its own bathroom and walk in closet. Has a good size backyard with mature trees and a sprinkler system. This home is in a prime location in Payette. Close to the middle school.  Nestled in a low traffic and quiet neighborhood.
